===環境===
據報導，從印度和世界各地來瑞詩凱詩的大量遊客正在消費大麻和酒精，並在海灘上半裸，導致人們抱怨該地區的精神環境受到影響<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.samaylive.com/gallery/photo-gallery/pics-it-s-goa-beach-of-rishikesh-foreign-tourists-nude-and-topless-take-sunbathing/620911/66613.html |title=PICS: ये है ऋषिकेश के गोवा बीच का नज़ारा, विदेशियों की बेशर्मी से आहत हो रही आस्था |trans-title=PICS: This is the view of Rishikesh's Goa beach, the belief that the foreigners are shocked by the shamelessness of the foreigners |website=Samaylive |access-date=12 June 2015 |archive-date=2015-04-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150416082951/http://www.samaylive.com/gallery/photo-gallery/pics-it-s-goa-beach-of-rishikesh-foreign-tourists-nude-and-topless-take-sunbathing/620911/66613.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.newindianexpress.com/lifestyle/travel/Where-Rishikesh-Meets-Goa/2015/03/22/article2721758.ece |title=Where Rishikesh Meets Goa |date=22 March 2015 |newspaper=The New Indian Express |access-date=12 June 2015 |archive-date=2016-06-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160626073008/http://www.newindianexpress.com/lifestyle/travel/Where-Rishikesh-Meets-Goa/2015/03/22/article2721758.ece |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="TOI-47437432">{{cite news |url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/Rafting-in-Ganga-promotes-obscene-activities-VHP-says-wants-it-banned/articleshow/47437432.cms |title=Rafting in Ganga promotes obscene activities, VHP says, wants it banned |first=Sheo S. |last=Jaiswal |date=27 May 2015 |newspaper=The Times of India |access-date=12 June 2015 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108094546/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/Rafting-in-Ganga-promotes-obscene-activities-VHP-says-wants-it-banned/articleshow/47437432.cms |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.andhraheadlines.com/news/national/146568/adventure-tours-rishikesh-end-up-in-rave-parties |title=Adventure tours @ Rishikesh end up in rave parties |website=Andhra Hea